      Mount Ommaney is one of western Brisbane's most established family suburbs, built around large blocks, quality construction and the retail amenity of Mount Ommaney Centre on Dandenong Road. The suburb consistently attracts families upgrading within the western corridor who want space, good schools and established streetscapes.
    </p>
