    <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column;">

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What drives property values in Mount Ommaney?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Mount Ommaney property values are driven by block size, position within the suburb, school catchments and quality of the original construction. The suburb's established character and proximity to Mount Ommaney Centre attract families upgrading within the western Brisbane corridor, and the comparison set spans Jindalee, Westlake and Riverhills.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          How long does it take to sell a home in Mount Ommaney?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Well-presented Mount Ommaney homes typically sell within 28 to 42 days. A property positioned accurately relative to Jindalee and Westlake comparables will generate strong inquiry in the first two weeks of a well-run campaign. The suburb draws a family buyer pool with genuine buying capacity from across the western Brisbane corridor.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What is the lifestyle like in Mount Ommaney?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Mount Ommaney offers established western Brisbane family living with excellent retail access at Mount Ommaney Centre, quiet tree-lined streets, Centenary Motorway connections to the CBD, and proximity to western Brisbane's parks and reserves. It suits families who want space, quality schooling and a settled suburban character.</p>
      </details>

      <details style="padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#191817; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          Is Mount Ommaney a good suburb to buy in right now?
          <span style="color:#b98229; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Mount Ommaney remains one of western Brisbane's most consistently sought-after family suburbs. Its established character, large lots and strong school catchments draw persistent demand from buyers upgrading from Jindalee, Riverhills and Middle Park, and the suburb's limited new supply supports steady long-term value.</p>
      </details>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

